showerReviews.reviewText:
this place is just superb, so well thought out and so much care put into it;
i love the toilet/shower block, clean but not smelling of chemicals, and there are warm showers and plenty of loos, i never had to wait to use them;
in an incredible location, with great facilities and everything you need on your doorstep;
highly recommend the park and ride to get into durham;
we will likely be returning in our campervan or tent sometime soon!

